	</p>
	
	<p>
		<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅ-koṇṭacōḻa-maṇṭalattu-p puḻaṟ-kōṭṭattu	
		<lb n="2"/>Uṭaiyār tiruvoṟṟiyūr-uṭaiyār kōyilil maṭam-uṭaiya caturāṉaṉa-paṇṭitaṉum <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>mā<hi rend="grantha">he</hi><gap unit="character" quantity="10" reason="lost"/>ṭāṉum <hi rend="grantha">śrī-</hi>kā<unclear>ri</unclear>yam Ariyapirāṉ paṭṭaṉum cōmacittāntam vakkāṇikkum vā<hi rend="grantha">gīśvara</hi>-paṇṭitaṉum kālum piṭāruñ ceyaṅ-koṇṭa-cōḻa-maṇṭala-piṭā<unclear>ra</unclear>ṉu
		<lb n="3" break="no"/>n tiruvoṟṟiyūr-<unclear>p</unclear> piccaṉuṅ kōyil nāyakam paṭampakka-nāyaka-paṭṭaṉum kōyiṟ-kaṇakku-t tiru<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="10"/>ṭ<supplied reason="lost">ai</supplied>yār tiru-p-paṅkūṉi y-uttirattu Āṟān tirunāḷ-āṉa putaṉ-kiḻamai<unclear>yu</unclear>m Ēkātaciyu<unclear>m</unclear> peṟṟa Āyil<choice><orig>ai</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>yattiṉaṉṟu paṭampakka-nāyaka-tēvar tirumakiḻiṉ kiṭ <!--@emfr:it does not make sense this kit. Maybe it's kita.--> tiruvōlakkañ ceyt' eḻuntaru
		<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḷi y-iruntu Āḷuṭaiya-nampi <hi rend="grantha">śr<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice></hi>-purāṇaṅ k<unclear>ē</unclear>ṭṭ’ aruḷā niṟka Uṭaiyār tēvatāṉam vaṭuka-p perum-pāk=kattu-k= kāṇi <gap quantity="10" unit="character" reason="lost"/> y-eṉṟu viṇṇappañ ceyya namm-<choice><orig>u</orig><reg>ū</reg></choice>rkaḷil I<unclear>ra</unclear>ṇ<choice><orig>ai</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>yūr Amuta<unclear>ṅ</unclear> kiḻavaṉ periyāṉ cōmaṉuk=ku-t taṇṭicaṉ vilai-y-āka viṟṟu-k kāṇi-y-āka-k koṭukka v-eṉṟu tiruvāymoḻi	
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>ntaruḷa Ivv-ūrkku-k kāṇi-vilai Aṉṟāṭu naṟ-kācu nūṟṟ' iru<unclear>pa</unclear>tum <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-paṇṭāratt' oṭukku-k koṇṭu
		Iv-va<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="8"/> <supplied reason="lost">ki</supplied>ḻavaṉ periyāṉ cōma<choice><orig>n</orig><reg>ṉ</reg></choice>ukku <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-paṇṭāratt' iṟai y-iṟukkavum
	</p>
	
	<p>
		Iva<choice><orig>n</orig><reg>ṉ</reg></choice>ukkum ivaṉ va<hi rend="grantha">ṃśa</hi>ttārkkum viṟṟōṟṟi <hi rend="grantha">pr<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>kraya</hi>ttukku<choice><orig>r</orig><reg>ṟ</reg></choice>itt’ āvat’ āka viṟṟu-k koṭuttōm
	</p>
	
	<p>
		Ip-paṭikku Ivai ma
		<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭam-uṭaiya caturā<choice><orig>nan</orig><reg>ṉaṉ</reg></choice>a-paṇṭitaṉ Eḻuttu <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paṭikku Ivai tiruv<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>tivē-y iṭaṅkoṇṭāṉ Eḻuttu <unclear><g type="gomutraFinal">.</g></unclear>
	</p>
	<p>
		<gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/>ṉ Eḻuttu <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paṭikku Ivai cōmacittāntam vakkāṇikkum vā<hi rend="grantha">gīśva</hi>ra-paṇṭitaṉ Eḻuttu <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>
	</p>
	<p>	
		Ip-paṭikku Ivai kālum piṭārañ ceyaṅ-koṇṭa-cōḻa-maṇṭala-piṭāraṉ Eḻuttu <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paṭi-k<lb n="7" break="no"/>ku Ivai tiruvoṟṟiyūr piccaṉ Eḻuttu <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g>
